	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Liv. 8.7. Put to death by his father, the Consul, for disobeying orders against single combats (Liv. 8.6-8; Cic. Fin. 1.23 and 34-5; 2.61; Off. 3.112; Sull. 33, and Schol. Bob. ad loc.; Sall. Cat. 52.30; Dion. Hal. 8.79.2; Verg. Aen. 6.824f. and Serv. ad loc.; Val. Max. 1.7.3; 2.7.6; 5.8.3; 6.4.1; 6.9.1; 9.3.4-5; Plut. Fab. 9.2; Par. Min. 12; Quintil.{137} Inst. Or. 5.11.7; Frontin. Str. 4.1.40-41; Flor. 1.14; App. Samn. 3; Gell. 1.13.7; 9.13.20; Dio fr. 35; Ampel. 18.4; Auct. Vir. Ill. 28.4; Zon. 7.26; see under Consuls)." .
